{"tid":434443,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返工俾人大粒串9 到飛起","createTime":"2017-10-13T09:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T09:40:46.000Z","uid":115776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2e22a3c0a54b16cf5cd918ed5882e4272c5e6c1f","tid":434443,"uid":115776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:23:52.000Z","msg":"做份跟本面面都唔討好的中間人的工<br />\n呢邊happy就另一邊嬲<br />\n跟住就得罪左個好串的大粒（其他dept)<br />\n平時都冇咩接觸<br />\n一有就串到我飛起<br />\n我嬲到面都紅埋， 已經記係心目中<br />\n其實如果要報仇， 係報到<br />\n但報完可能佢仲憎9我， 對我冇咩利<br />\n有冇d咩高明d手法， 可以做9佢， 但又係符合辦公室政治"},{"pid":"2779e75d37d3b814fb8724758eca89fb1260c555","tid":434443,"uid":44415,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:25:12.000Z","msg":"女人流幾滴馬尿就可以唔使俾人鬧"},{"pid":"2600059da636863eeead51ed8a40245c43dbbbd0","tid":434443,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:25:27.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"45d05ff3667a68228977587be97d7b3285976b49","tid":434443,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:26:55.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪西面八婆先 ?"},{"pid":"a952e940fab7150579c7b5ca8ba72762a8019548","tid":434443,"uid":115776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:30:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係咪西面八婆先 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要西可以好西<br />\n但個大粒係咩都會串係一餐果d<br />\n果果都知佢份人好撚記仇<br />\n避得就避果種"},{"pid":"ca49afac761abd9770289231f1ff4d1afaf13382","tid":434443,"uid":115776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:32:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係咪西面八婆先 ?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zej918df\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzej918df&h=18a8d6ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"333edb3f4d41825f53dcebd7c6ce819af0700aed","tid":434443,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主係咪西面八婆先 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要西可以好西<br />\n但個大粒係咩都會串係一餐果d<br />\n果果都知佢份人好撚記仇<br />\n避得就避果種</blockquote><br />\n人地大粒過你咁多, 你玩唔起, 忍下喇~"},{"pid":"6ca0c346dc6822b2efe85905b6993c6144709649","tid":434443,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:33:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主係咪西面八婆先 ?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zej918df\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzej918df&h=18a8d6ad&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩屌.jpg"},{"pid":"8b1744f448e98ec32b427232e6c3f27c203197cc","tid":434443,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:35:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主係咪西面八婆先 ?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zej918df\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzej918df&h=18a8d6ad&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩屌.jpg</blockquote><br />\n算啦 唔好搞咁多野。除非你好有手段啦"},{"pid":"0e5e277089098f94a4844f71c5b435b144df0576","tid":434443,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:36:55.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩 自貼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4eea23c828ea41d6f83407aa913daa8aa990350","tid":434443,"uid":115776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:39:03.000Z","msg":"唔小心貼左係snapchat cap人張相出來<br />\nsor"},{"pid":"bbe7a2f126f9bb6684fddc3ff943805f9cab4a6e","tid":434443,"uid":134260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:40:46.000Z","msg":"咁樓豬好難怪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你的樣子如何"}]}